sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant IndividualProvidedDetailsController
    participant HMRC_Auth as HMRC Auth
    participant MongoDB as MongoDB (individual)

    Client->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: DELETE /individual-provided-details/delete-by-id/{individualProvidedDetailsId}
    IndividualProvidedDetailsController->>HMRC_Auth: Authenticate (GG, Agent affinity)
    alt Auth fails
        HMRC_Auth-->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: 401 Unauthorised
        IndividualProvidedDetailsController-->>Client: 401 Unauthorised
    else Auth succeeds
        HMRC_Auth-->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: Authenticated
        IndividualProvidedDetailsController->>MongoDB: removeById(individualProvidedDetailsId)
        MongoDB-->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: Deleted (or not found — idempotent)
        IndividualProvidedDetailsController-->>Client: 200 OK
    end
